comments.body:
BB support in Alloy will be available in 1.2.0. At this time, 1.2.0 exists only on the master branch of the github repo. It can be installed like this:

{code}
[sudo] npm install -g git://github.com/appcelerator/alloy.git
{code}

Plans are being made for perhaps an intermediate release of Alloy, but this will be handled outside the scope of this ticket.
